{"tid":85592,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇戒糖既人可以入黎分享下","createTime":"2017-01-18T12:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T16:28:39.000Z","uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b1852dcf41a817723d06ca9198759bd432c2d22","tid":85592,"uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:28:59.000Z","msg":"一直都覺得自己好似有啲糖上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日都不受控咁去食啲高糖分既甜野<br />\n有冇人過來人可以分享下戒糖既過程同成效<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c5492e39e0663af697b2504ddf64ba28e086a3","tid":85592,"uid":44787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:36:20.000Z","msg":"呢邊小食當戒<br />\n口痕就食香口膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4095cc891416a6c4329da9136352f12a3765380f","tid":85592,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:37:36.000Z","msg":"有一排好似糖中毒，塊面生好多野。<br />\n最緊要係唔好成日係出面飲野，飯就少汁，多飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bff8e5977a41731bec0ad6771a98384ce5331a6","tid":85592,"uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:33:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢邊小食當戒<br />\n口痕就食香口膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過食薄荷糖代替零食<br />\n發覺唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffaccb1e3cea4da7952119f8b8b3df772d93ad35","tid":85592,"uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:34:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有一排好似糖中毒，塊面生好多野。<br />\n最緊要係唔好成日係出面飲野，飯就少汁，多飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食得多零食塊面真係差咁啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a322f0f9512f61672c8a363e7897438ae7b14c38","tid":85592,"uid":25280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:36:07.000Z","msg":"唔好食甜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食完個口酸酸地"},{"pid":"1a9db59729f4e3105e51116602cc3f49715330e4","tid":85592,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T04:17:11.000Z","msg":"點可能戒糖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c9af5faa4390bbf537c6c4849932fd9e0ba840","tid":85592,"uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T04:31:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點可能戒糖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講緊係減少糖分吸收<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我相信都市人應該大多數超標<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2dfe3bc210416951580b52094d4fddb4e6988f","tid":85592,"uid":10620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:54:58.000Z","msg":"戒下戒下就會覺得齋啡，奶茶檸茶唔落糖幾好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5f5615b705b845c75b1dc558cf8a49681af9b9","tid":85592,"uid":2141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:57:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戒下戒下就會覺得齋啡，奶茶檸茶唔落糖幾好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時反而仲會覺得甜嘢食到嗰口好痴笠笠 <br />\n或者好甜好難飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0804b743ae068a89a7dc7ea05d0daf3ed498abc4","tid":85592,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:58:18.000Z","msg":"平時食開重糖點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff6ce10fae2fde6a497e6748893e20479b55b66","tid":85592,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:58:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d654704a566d30ea99ef9ed37785b7cf627828f","tid":85592,"uid":53707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T12:06:02.000Z","msg":"係呀 人唔食糖就好暈"},{"pid":"21b08a04487feade9c02d3d0a080e72e12332f94","tid":85592,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T12:12:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點可能戒糖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講緊係減少糖分吸收<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我相信都市人應該大多數超標<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來戒字係咁解？"},{"pid":"3d60b76d919443387f097aa3ccd2686d2e52c177","tid":85592,"uid":55731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T16:28:39.000Z","msg":"本身唔中意食甜品<br />\n有d甜少少既雪糕都覺得好難食<br />\n但係有時都會食下生果同糖"}]}